@node history "History"

 
       V1.1 - The first version.

       V2.0 - New generation Poem:
              (Stardate 6978.3.5)

              o Now support only KS2.04+ machines.
              o Code optimized (use now only one datafile).
              o Added option -p
              o Added HangUp check.
              o Used Amigaguide format (Docs).

@endnode

